:<font size="15">גּלילה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
גּלילה  -  גּליל / gâlîyl  gâlîylâh / gaw-leel', gaw-lee-law'

===Etymology===
The same as [[גּליל]] {{HH|1550}}; a circle (with the article); 

===Proper noun===
'''גּלילה'''

# Galil (as a special circuit) in the North of Palestine: - [[Galilee]].

